        <hr/>
                        
<div class="txt-block" id="name-bio-text">
        <div class="name-trivia-bio-text">
                      <div class="inline" itemprop="description">
Bryan Singer was born on September 17, 1965 in New York City, New York, USA as Bryan Jay Singer. He is a producer and director, known for <a href="/title/tt0412142?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk1">House M.D.</a> (2004), <a href="/title/tt0114814?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk2">The Usual Suspects</a> (1995) and <a href="/title/tt0290334?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk3">X2</a> (2003).            <span class="see-more inline nobr-only">
                    <a href="/name/nm0001741/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm"
>See full bio</a> &raquo;
            </span>
</div>        </div>
</div>

                        
    <div id="name-born-info" class="txt-block">
