    <h2>Personal Details</h2>
        <div id="details-other-works" class="see-more inline canwrap">
                <h4 class="inline">Other Works:</h4>
June 2006 - DC Comics publishes a four-part "Superman Returns" prequel mini- series, with story by Bryan Singer, <a href="/name/nm1002424?ref_=nm_pdt_wrk1">Michael Dougherty</a> and <a href="/name/nm0003529?ref_=nm_pdt_wrk2">Dan Harris</a>.                    <span class="see-more inline">
                        <a href="/name/nm0001741/otherworks?ref_=nm_pdt_wrk_sm"
>See more</a> 
                    </span>
                    &raquo;
